title: Seehausen (Uckermark) station
text:
Seehausen (Uckermark) () is a railway station in the village of <a href="Seehausen%2C%20Uckermark">Seehausen</a>, municipality <a href="Oberuckersee">Oberuckersee</a>, <a href="Brandenburg">Brandenburg</a>, <a href="Germany">Germany</a>. The station lies of the <a href="Angerm%C3%BCnde%E2%80%93Stralsund%20railway">Angermünde–Stralsund railway</a> and the train services are operated by <a href="Deutsche%20Bahn">Deutsche Bahn</a>.
